@startuml UC5_SearchSortFilterBorrowedDevices_Detail

title UC5 - Search / Filter Borrowed Devices (No User)

actor User

boundary MyDevicesPage
control MyDevicesViewModel
control GetBorrowedDevicesUseCase

control IDeviceRepository
control DeviceRepository
control IDeviceDataSource
control DeviceDataSource

database SQLite

User -> MyDevicesPage : Enter search / filter
MyDevicesPage -> MyDevicesViewModel : OnQueryChanged(query)

MyDevicesViewModel -> GetBorrowedDevicesUseCase : Execute(query)

GetBorrowedDevicesUseCase -> IDeviceRepository : GetByStatus(Borrowed, query)

IDeviceRepository -> DeviceRepository
DeviceRepository -> IDeviceDataSource : Query with conditions
IDeviceDataSource -> DeviceDataSource
DeviceDataSource -> SQLite : Query status=Borrowed + filter
SQLite --> DeviceDataSource

DeviceDataSource --> DeviceRepository
DeviceRepository --> GetBorrowedDevicesUseCase : List<Device>

GetBorrowedDevicesUseCase --> MyDevicesViewModel : PagedResult<Device>
MyDevicesViewModel --> MyDevicesPage : Update list
MyDevicesPage --> User : Display filtered result

@enduml
